Authentication method in postgresql administration


 local         DATABASE  USER IP_ADDRESS METHOD  [OPTIONS]
 host          DATABASE  USER  ADDRESS  METHOD  [OPTIONS]
 hostssl       DATABASE  USER  ADDRESS  METHOD  [OPTIONS]
 hostnossl     DATABASE  USER  ADDRESS  METHOD  [OPTIONS]
 hostgssenc    DATABASE  USER  ADDRESS  METHOD  [OPTIONS]
 hostnogssenc  DATABASE  USER  ADDRESS  METHOD  [OPTIONS]
pg_hba.conf = Host-Based Authentication Configuration file
It displays the location (path) of the Host-Based Authentication file used by PostgreSQL.
show hba_file;
              hba_file              
------------------------------------
 /var/lib/pgsql/17/data/pg_hba.conf

